title: Running the Canyon
text: Reaction: After a Speeder or Fighter unit you control is focused to strike, discard an event card from your hand to have that unit gain [Unit Damage] ([Edge-Enabled Blast Damage]) until the end of the strike.

title: Luke's T-16 Skyhopper
text:
Targeted strike.
Reaction: After you play an event card, deal 1 damage to a target enemy objective. (Limit once per turn.)

title: Memories of Home
text:
Action: Place 1 shield on a target friendly unit.
Reaction: After you win a Force struggle by 2 or more Force icons, return this event from your discard pile to your hand.

title: Bull's-eye!
text: Action: During an engagement, target a friendly unit that has targeted strike. That unit strikes immediately.

title: Target of Opportunity
text: If you are the attacking player, deal 1 damage to the engaged objective.

title: Tiny Robotic Sociopath
text: While you control a Specter unit, each player cannot draw more than 5 cards during his draw phase.

title: Chopper
text: Reaction: After a card is discarded from an opponent's hand, deal 1 damage to a target unit controlled by that player. (Limit once per turn.)

title: Captured Courier Droid
text: Reaction: After this unit enters play, a target opponent must choose and discard 1 card from his hand.

title: Electroshock Prod
text:
Enhance a Specter or Droid unit. Enhanced unit gains [Unit Damage].
Reaction: After a phase begins, focus this enhancement to treat a target unit's printed text box as if it were blank (except for Traits) until the end of the phase.

title: Makeshift Repairs
text: Action: Search your deck for an enhancement, reveal it, and add it to your hand. If your opponent has 0 cards in hand, search for any card instead. Shuffle your deck.

title: Improvised Tactics
text: Action: Search your deck for a Specter unit and put it into play. Then, shuffle a Specter unit you control into its owner's deck.

title: The Emperor's Shadow
text: Reaction: After you play an enhancement, draw 1 card. (Limit once per turn.)

title: The Emperor's Shuttle
text:
Shielding.
Reaction: After the Force phase begins, sacrifice an enhancement attached to this unit to remove 1 focus token from a target friendly unit.

title: Shuttle Pilot
text: Pilot (1). (Enhanced Vehicle unit gains edge (1).)

title: The Emperor's Favor
text:
Enhance a [Sith] unit.
Enhanced unit gains [Unit Damage] and +1 damage capacity.
Action: Play this enhancement from your discard pile.

title: Sensor Array
text:
Enhance your play area.
Interrupt: When an event card is played, focus this enhancement and discard an enhancement from your hand to cancel that event's effects.

title: Well Equipped
text: Remove 1 token (any type) from a unit or objective card you control with 1 or more enhancements on it.

title: Technological Terror
text:
Imperial Navy affiliation only.
Elite.
While this objective is undamaged, the Death Star dial is considered to be 1 point higher.

title: Death Star
text:
Elite.
Shielding.
Targeted strike. Cannot be affected by enemy card effects. Damage dealt by this unit cannot be prevented or redirected.
While this unit is not participating in an engagement, it cannot have focus tokens placed on it by enemy tactics icons.
This unit gains [Unit Damage] [Blast Damage] for each point on the Death Star dial.

title: Death Star Engineer
text:
Resources generated by this unit can only be used to play Space Station or Capital Ship units.
Action: During the deployment phase, sacrifice this unit to remove 1 focus token from a target Space Station or Capital Ship unit.

Action: During the deployment phase, sacrifice this unit to remove 1 focus token from a target Space Station or Capital Ship unit.

title: Control Room
text:
Enhance your play area.
Limited. (You cannot play more than one limited card per turn.)

title: Heart of Cold
text:
Scum and Villainy affiliation only.
Reaction: After you reveal 1 or more [Scum and Villainy] fate cards in your edge stack, remove 1 damage from a target [Scum and Villainy] objective.

title: IG-88C
text: Reaction: After an enemy card effect that targeted this unit resolves or after 1 or more tokens are placed on this unit by enemy combat icons, capture a target exhausted enemy unit. (Limit once per turn.)

title: FEX-model Combat Droid
text: Forced Reaction: After this unit is declared as an attacker or defender, an opponent may focus his affiliation card to remove this unit from the engagement.

title: Ugnaught
text: Reaction: After a card is captured, remove 1 damage from a friendly Vehicle or Droid unit.

title: Tricks and Nonsense
text: If your opponent's edge stack contains 1 or more [Smugglers and Spies] or neutral cards, your opponent cannot trigger abilities during this engagement.
